  "slug": "swem",
  "title": "Star Worm Equestrian Mod",
  "description": "Upgrading everything Minecraft Equestrian",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1020320292012298300/discord_header2.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 90px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>We are Star Worm Equestrian Mod (SWEM)! </strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>Upgrading everything Minecraft Equestrian. Model, tack, animations, armor, decor. All of it and soon to be more!</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #993300;\"><em><strong>For details, suggestions, and questions - check the spoilers down below or visit our wiki/discord!</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #993300;\"><em><strong>Bugs must be reported to our Github.</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #ff6600;\"><em><strong>---------&nbsp; THIS MOD REQUIRES <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib/files/4052293\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GECKOLIB</a> 3.0.100+ &amp; <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/playeranimator\">PLAYERANIMATOR</a> 0.3.5+1.16.5&nbsp; ---------</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff9900;\">Current Version: 1.16.5, Phase One [FORGE]</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1019996251326001172/2022-09-08_23.21.26-removebg-preview_1_1.png\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021033698126209054/1-removebg-preview.png\" /></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Our&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #ff9900; text-decoration: underline;\"><b>★&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\">additions to the game:</span></b></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">✮ Custom model and <strong>animations</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ Separate <strong>gaits</strong>!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ <strong>Training</strong> and bonding</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ Colored variants and full sets of functional <strong>English, Western and Adventure Tack</strong>!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;✧ <em>Bridles, Saddles, Girths, Blankets, Leg Wraps, Earnets, Breastcollars! Complete with Saddle, Bridle, and Armor Racks.</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ <strong>Pasture Blankets</strong> and Armored Pasture Blankets in 16 colors!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ 112 Coats in game!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;✧ <em>From bays to grays to splashes and more... and secrets?</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ Functional <strong>armor</strong> with wings + extra cosmetic horse armors. (Flight not yet implemented)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ <strong>Foals</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">✮ <strong>Food and Water Systems</strong>!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;✧ <em>Functional feeders, buckets and troughs</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">✮<strong>&nbsp;Stall Doors</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">✮ <strong>And more...</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 120px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1020002728388341850/2022-09-08_23.25.19-removebg-preview_1.png\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 180px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1020342977027125268/2022-09-08_23.35.59-removebg-preview_1.png\" width=\"451\" height=\"170\" /></strong></span></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1063801393644830730/4.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021033697601933413/2-removebg-preview.png\" /></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><em><strong>Here is a showcase of some (not all) of our custom animated horse model and player!</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Walk</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/738913921871904829/1020049466490900572/walkswem.gif\" width=\"531\" height=\"453\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Trot</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/738913921871904829/1020050717114900570/trotswem.gif\" width=\"535\" height=\"456\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Canter</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/738913921871904829/1020051369031381022/canterswem.gif\" width=\"531\" height=\"453\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Gallop</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/738913921871904829/1020052525992386620/gallopswem.gif\" width=\"521\" height=\"445\" /></p>\n<p><strong>One of our 5 levels of jump!</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/738913921871904829/1021197761535807559/jumplvl5swem.gif\" width=\"756\" height=\"401\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1063801393196060762/3.png\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021033697190883361/3-removebg-preview.png\" /></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><strong>A trailer for our recreation of Spirit: Stallion of Cimarron, by Redzeal. Coming soon to our official youtube!</strong></p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZUU04z9j1TQ\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Check out Peachy's '10 reasons why I love SWEM' video! It showcases our in-game items, tack, and jumps + how to use them!</strong></p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iaeEkmGILv8\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>An episode of Redzeal's SWEM based RRP series!</strong></p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VED1VTRu63Y\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Brooke's short and sweet guide on looking after your SWEM ponies &lt;3</strong></p>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/v_bmVz-As0A\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1063801395297407047/2.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1044356132619161640/Features__4_-removebg-preview.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><strong>Pull requests are welcome. For significant changes, please open an issue first to discuss what you would like to change.</strong></p>\n<p><em>Click the icon for SWE/M's github!</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/AlaharranHonor/SWEquestrianM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GitHub-Logo.png\" alt=\"GitHub Logo, symbol, meaning, history, PNG, brand\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1044356124712911019/Untitled_design_-_2022-11-21T205747.958.png\" width=\"881\" height=\"220\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021033696775651409/4-removebg-preview.png\" /></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><strong>Q: Will you stay in 1.16.5? Will you backport to 1.12 or update to 1.18+?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> We are currently in 1.16.5 but will soon move onto working on 1.18 and potentially any other future updates. However, we will not be backporting to 1.12 due to a series of development related conflicts and factors.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Q: Will there be a server for the mod?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, we are and will be working on an official server and modpack. To hear updates on this, make sure to join or discord linked below or keep up to date on our progress through our website.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Q: Please can I have a custom coat?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> We will be working on opening commissions for custom coats ingame. These costs have not been finalised, join our discord to hear more.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Q: I have a suggestion for the mod! Where may I contact you?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> In our discord, we have a channel dedicated to our suggestions. There you may also search for previous suggestions and our plans to instate said suggestions.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Q: What are the phases and what are we on?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Phase One is our&nbsp;Adventure Release. Focused on upgrading everything horse for survival mode. Horse model, coats, animations, skill levelling, stable care, training equipment, horse armor, and equestrian decor.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Phase Two is our&nbsp;English/Western Release. Focussed on fluffing equestrian servers with all those pleasantries and upgrades. More saddles, more tack, more horse models, more animations, more decorations, more coats, breeding and genetics, illnesses, and options.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Phase Three is our&nbsp;Alight Release. Did anyone say <em>magic</em>? The biggest and last release will be completely based on adventure. A prebuild dimension with lore, layers of exploration, new blocks, new mobs and mythical equines, and new things to discover.</p>\n<p>.</p>\n<p><strong>Q: How may I donate?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Donations to support development and the team can be made through our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ko-fi.com/swem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">Ko-fi</span></a>&nbsp;or to the owner's&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/swem/settings/paypal.me/hannturpinswem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PayPal</a></span>&nbsp;. More information on these and their purposes/perks can be found in our discord's how-to-help channel &lt;3</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Q: How do I download mods? What are this mod's dependencies?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;Please use Google or Youtube to find out how to download forge and mods. This mod requires geckolib and playeranimator.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/737144919717707896/1007696884653113436/htrdj.gif\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1063801394135584789/5.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021892455194427442/Features__1_-removebg-preview.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><strong><em>Credits:</em></strong></span><br /><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Owner and Production Lead&nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>AlaharranHonor<br /><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Dev&nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>Legenden (Primary)<br /><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Resources and Textures&nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>SWE/M Texture and Model Art Team<br /><em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;See website for full credits list.</em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em><strong>Rights:</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Under SWE/M&nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>All Rights Reserved<br /><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Code&nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>If you'd like help with your code or would like to help SWE/M, please contact us! We are closed to public but still want to help other programmers!<br /><br /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em><strong>Modpacks and Videos:</strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Can I use this in my modpack(s)?&nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span><strong>Yes!</strong> No credit is required but please contact us so we can play too!<br /><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Can I make a video using SWEM? &nbsp; &nbsp;||&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes!&nbsp;</strong></span>Let us know so we can report it for our community to see!</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>-----&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #003300;\"><em>Don't forget that Star Worm Lighting Mod and Star Worm Decor Mod are built to go with the SWEM mod!</em></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 120px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/swdm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021044562120155176/SW_DECO_M__5_-removebg-preview.png\" width=\"303\" height=\"106\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/swlm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021044562627674112/SW_DECO_M__4_-removebg-preview.png\" width=\"303\" height=\"106\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1063802471597752411/Untitled_design_62.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><em>&nbsp;Stay up-to-date on our socials!</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.discord.gg/swem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://www.freepnglogos.com/uploads/discord-logo-png/discord-logo-logodownload-download-logotipos-1.png\" alt=\"Discord Logo Png - Free Transparent PNG Logos\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/StarWormEquestrian\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1384/1384060.png\" alt=\"Youtube - Free social media icons\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.swequestrian.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://www.freepnglogos.com/uploads/logo-website-png/logo-website-file-globe-icon-svg-wikimedia-commons-21.png\" alt=\"Website Logo PNG, Web Site Logos Free Download - Free Transparent PNG Logos\" width=\"54\" height=\"54\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/starwormequestrian/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Instagram_icon.png/2048px-Instagram_icon.png\" alt=\"File:Instagram icon.png - Wikimedia Commons\" width=\"53\" height=\"53\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/swem/settings/discord.gg/swem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br /><br /><br /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021038522783776808/2022-09-18_13.40.52-removebg-preview.png\" width=\"393\" height=\"182\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/855104943287304222/1021353552003735663/Untitled_design__87_-removebg-preview_1.png\" width=\"429\" height=\"177\" /></p>",
